- ASF fixes
- put_seek bug fix


version 0.3.1: added avi/divx support

- added AVI support
- added MPEG-4 codec compatible with OpenDivX. It is based on the H.263 codec
- added sound for flash format (not tested)


version 0.3: initial public release
